import React from "react";
import { Button, Card, Col, Container, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import "./CardForm.css";

export default function CardForm(props) {
  return (
    <Container className="d-flex vh-100">
      <Row className="m-auto align-self-center">
        <Col>
          <Card className="Card">
            <Card.Header as="h3" className="card-header">
              Form data
            </Card.Header>
            <Card.Body>
              <Form className="form">
                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">Tema Undangan</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Select>
                    <option>Silakan Pilih Tema</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </Form.Select>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">Bahasa Undangan</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Select>
                    <option>Silakan Pilih Bahasa</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </Form.Select>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">Paket Undangan</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Select>
                    <option>Silakan Pilih Paket</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </Form.Select>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">
                    Menggunakan Foto
                  </Form.Label>
                  <Form.Select>
                    <option>Pilih</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </Form.Select>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">Email address</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Enter email" />
                  <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                    We'll never share your email with anyone else.
                  </Form.Text>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                  <Form.Label className="labelForm">Password</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Password" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                  <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                  Submit
                </Button>
              </Form>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}
